bdflashSize.name: bdflashSize
bdflashSize.description: Total Size in Octets of Flash memory

bdflashFree.name: bdflashFree
bdflashFree.description: Unused Size in Octets of Flash memory

bdflashController.name: bdflashController
bdflashController.description: Provides the type of Flash controller (either CCTL or CCTL2) installed in the router.

bdflashCard.name: bdflashCard
bdflashCard.description: Provides the type of Flash Card installed in the router. For example, the type of Flash Card could be either CSC-MS or CSC-MC+.

bdflashVPP.name: bdflashVPP
bdflashVPP.description: State of the VPP DIP jumper on the Flash memory card. Files can be written to the Flash memory card only if the VPP DIP jumper is turned on.

bdflashEraseTime.name: bdflashEraseTime
bdflashEraseTime.description: Indicates the value of sysUptime the last time Flash memory was erased. If the flash had not been erased after powerup it has a value of 0 days 00:00:00.

bdflashEraseStatus.name: bdflashEraseStatus
bdflashEraseStatus.description: Status of current or last flash erasing

bdflashToNet.name: bdflashToNet
bdflashToNet.description: Write flash entry to tftp server. Value should be the name of the flash entry to send. Instance is the IP address of the tftp host.

bdflashToNetTime.name: bdflashToNetTime
bdflashToNetTime.description: Indicates the value of sysUpTime the last time a file was transfered from Flash memory on the router to a TFTP host. Returns 0 days 00:00:00 if there had been no transfer since powerup.

bdflashToNetStatus.name: bdflashToNetStatus
bdflashToNetStatus.description: Status of current or last flash to net transfer

bdnetToFlash.name: bdnetToFlash
bdnetToFlash.description: Write flash entry from tftp server. Value should be the name of the flash entry to write. Instance is the IP address of the tftp host.

bdnetToFlashTime.name: bdnetToFlashTime
bdnetToFlashTime.description: Indicates the value of sysUpTime the last time file was copied from a Trivial File Transfer Protocol(TFTP) server to the Flash memory on the router. Returns 0 days 00:00:00 if there had been no transfers since powerup.

bdnetToFlashStatus.name: bdnetToFlashStatus
bdnetToFlashStatus.description: Status of current or last net to flash transfer

bdflashStatus.name: bdflashStatus
bdflashStatus.description: Status of the availability of flash

bdflashEntries.name: bdflashEntries
bdflashEntries.description: Number of entries in the flash directory

bdlflashFileDirTable.name: bdlflashFileDirTable
bdlflashFileDirTable.description: A list of flash file entries.

bdlflashFileDirEntry.name: bdlflashFileDirEntry
bdlflashFileDirEntry.description: A collection of flash eprom objects

bdflashDirName.name: bdflashDirName
bdflashDirName.description: Name associated with the flash entry

bdflashDirSize.name: bdflashDirSize
bdflashDirSize.description: Size in Octets of a flash entry

bdflashDirStatus.name: bdflashDirStatus
bdflashDirStatus.description: Indicates the status of the entry
